      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IMPOSTER (1) goes very well at the course with three wins and a placing from seven starts. Scored by 7 lengths last time (22.48) in a Grade 5 over 390m at this track. Rates a leading player. LEKTRA ROSA (3) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 5th (25.87) at Ballarat. Has a strong winning record here at this journey. Cannot be left out. INTUITIVE (7) was in the minors two back (18.14) at Mt Gambier but ran below best last time at this track, finishing 7th. Has a good record here at this journey. The form from her last run stacks up well. Cannot be taken lightly. SAINT RAINE (4) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
